These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, juice
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, montecristo
City: miami, edinburgh, london
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person traveling to miami##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage          | mirinda      | fanta        | juice     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | ritmeester       | montecristo |
| City         | miami  | edinburgh      | london    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, chess
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, bellflower
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, may
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
6. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who growsrose and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Hobby           | cooking    | chess | sudoku |
| Flower   | rose | azalea       | bellflower   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Birthday         | february | may       | august   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, cola
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, paramedic, electrician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, havana, old-henry
1. the electrician is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the person drinking 7up and the old-henry-smoker##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
6. the electrician is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Beverage   | cola     | soy-milk | 7up |
| Job           | paramedic       | social-worker   | electrician    |
| Cigar     | old-henry      | swisher   | havana |

