.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, january
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, skiing
House: futuristic, craftsman, tower
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the craftsman house##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Birthday         | may  | september       | january |
| Sport           | skiing     | swimming      | baseball   |
| House   | craftsman | futuristic | tower     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

