.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
3 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, poker
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, sudoku, video-games
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, craftsman
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the craftsman house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Game           | scrabble | canasta | poker |
| Hobby   | video-games      | sudoku   | gardening            |
| House   | farmhouse   | craftsman  | ranch-style         |

