.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, craftsman
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, prince, alhambra
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, brown, black
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the prince-smoker and the art-deco house##2
2. the person who likes white is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person watching western movies is the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the person who likes white is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes white is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| House          | craftsman    | farmhouse     | art-deco |
| Cigar           | prince | alhambra | blend      |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery       | disaster    |
| Color   | brown      | white         | black     |

