The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, lily
1. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who likes apricot##2
7. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
