.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, bridge
House: victorian, farmhouse, tower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, rock, house
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram
1. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
3. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of rock##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
7. the victorian house is between the fan of rock and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Game      | snooker | scrabble    | bridge  |
| House         | tower        | victorian   | farmhouse   |
| Music-Genre   | house       | punk    | rock |
| Transport     | tram          | quad-bike | car       |

