3. the teacher is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing go is the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
6. the dancer is in an odd position##4
7. the dancer is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Job           | dancer     | teacher    | freelancer |
| Game   | go  | poker | mah-jongg      |
| Sport   | basketball       | parkour   | handball    |
| Color     | pink | emerald        | grey     |

