4. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
