.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
House: tower, ranch-style, cottage
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, documentary, horror
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, parkour
3 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, horse
1. the tower house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
2. the tower house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
3. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the horse##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| House           | tower | ranch-style   | cottage |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | documentary    | horror    |
| Sport         | cricket    | badminton | parkour   |
| Pet     | mouse  | horse     | turtle  |

