3. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching time-travel movies is between the police-officer and the bluemaster-smoker##2
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

