3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the palace house is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| House          | palace  | townhouse   | cape-cod |
