3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Job           | dancer  | police-officer | musician   |
| City   | edinburgh | london           | hamburg      |
| Game           | canasta   | snooker          | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero    | satire           | zombie |

 